data.description:
This is it! OWNER CARRY OPTION W/ AS LITTLE AS 10% DOWN ON APPROVED CREDIT.  MORE DOWN PAYMENT, THE LESS THE INTEREST RATE.  SELLER IS READY TO NEGOTIATE AS LOW AS 2% INTEREST RATE! CALL FOR DETAILS. 
 This contemporary 2004 custom Walston home has over 2500 sq. ft of living space, 4 bds and 2 bathrooms. Step in to the kitchen with warm kitchen cabinetry, and sleek-black granite countertops. Throughout the home is oversized rooms, extended ceiling height, carpets and ceramic tile. Additionally it has an oversized garage, and large lot on just shy of an acre. VIEWS of the Huachuca Mountains! Ready to call this your next home? Stop by today and take a look at this wonderful home.  Home starts here!
